{"tid":865797,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"一年開三次　反映政經困局","createTime":"2018-10-17T11:05:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-18T01:24:02.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"cc25b933ed9ce190635359ffa75331e7f4880390","tid":865797,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T11:05:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20181017/20523899\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181017%2F20523899&d=Y3ZsFMX1E4J%2BgR5VcGcqDQKEmdudW1rq3V1Y15kzxIU%3D&h=de10b38d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181017%2F20523899&h=5ab9cf1f\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20181017/20523899</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年10月17日 <br />\n<br />\n一年開三次　反映政經困局<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20181017/large/chris88.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20181017%2Flarge%2Fchris88.jpg&h=034e12fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n習近平<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【話你知】<br />\n<br />\n中共一般每5年召開一次大會，至今為第十九屆。而在兩次大會之間一般會舉行被稱為「中全會」的中央委員全體會議，通常是每一屆召開7次中全會。<br />\n<br />\n去年10月十九大甫一結束便按照慣例在第二天召開一中全會。其後，中共在轉年的1月召開二中全會討論「習思想」入憲和其他修憲問題，一個月後又召開了三中全會討論中共和國家領導人的換屆問題。<br />\n<br />\n而實際上，按照慣例三中全會本應在年底召開。如果今年內再召開四中全會，則2018年中共開了3次中全會，可謂打破中共以往慣例。歷史上這種情況只在毛時代的1958年出現過一次，今次破例或顯示目前政經困局對於中共的緊迫性。  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n「習權」後首次中全會　考驗治國智慧<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n受賄做兩面人　軍老虎房峰輝被踢出黨<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「習權」後首次中全會考驗治國智慧<br />\n<br />\n中共內外交困　傳急開四中全會月底舉行　商貿戰對策"},{"pid":"049d91a14931c3be2db552b7a01a04c2f71e4654","tid":865797,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T11:47:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f99e8a9af69bf9a1995e9404daa03e3c78d76b5","tid":865797,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T00:43:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bc2d9c991966cb507e49e128f46a5cfa69598e5","tid":865797,"uid":103513,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T01:20:35.000Z","msg":"開幾多會都係晒氣<br />\n咪又係變擦鞋大賽<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔通有人敢話國家就快唔掂，習種政策出錯咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf669a1dfc7f1429b1546e4d0171677316174c82","tid":865797,"uid":42921,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6bc2d9c991966cb507e49e128f46a5cfa69598e5","tid":865797,"uid":103513,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T01:20:35.000Z","msg":"開幾多會都係晒氣<br />\n咪又係變擦鞋大賽<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔通有人敢話國家就快唔掂，習種政策出錯咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T01:24:02.000Z","msg":"沒有 沒有 沒有 通過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}